claim.claim-text:
A portable food processor comprising

a container adapted for receiving food, a food processing member being mounted inside the said container adapted for being rotated relative to the said container and a container cover member adapted for covering the opening of the said container;

the said container cover member comprising a cover, a driving device adapted for being mounted on the top of the said cover and a transmission device adapted for being mounted inside the said cover;

the said transmission device adapted for being driven by the said driving device; the said food processing member adapted for being driven by the said transmission device;

the said food processing member adapted for being rotated relative to the said container;

the said driving device comprising a pull rod member;

the said pull rod member comprising a sliding track being arranged on the top of the said cover, a pull rod being mounted inside the said sliding track; and

the said pull rod comprising a gear rack for engaging the said transmission device.
